il --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/852.php" target="top">1.62A</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - The first part of this large patch. this patch concentrates on Hibernian spellcasters and hybrids, and introduces the change of Shamans Endurance Regain line from a &quot;cast&quot; buff with a timer, to a concentration buff.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/854.php" target="top">1.62B</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Second part patch. This patch is the first one directed at the Light Tanks, and includes the reduction to Left Axe (and the reasoning), the explanation and definition of the light tanks, the new dirty tricks/triple wield abilitys and the allowance of the hibernian race of Celts to become Nightshades.<br>
<br>
*A note on this. In the description of why Left Axe was getting a decrease in damage, this was said - &quot;In general, we try to find ways around directly reducing the damage done by specific classes by introducing counters usable by other classes, but in this case the imbalance is just too great&quot;. I find this to be an interesting way of creating class balance, and would explain some of mythics past actions.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/855.php" target="top">1.62C</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Third part. Contains the fix to the parry/block bug (more members in a group made it harder for the opponent(s) to block/parry), Two bolt fixes and a correction to the new Mercenary's Dirty Tricks ability.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/865.php" target="top">1.62D</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Fourth part. This one contains changes/additions for Archery classes and Pet Users, increased side degree arch on players, more changes to Hibernian casters, a /level change and some more light tank tweaks.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/866.php" target="top">1.62E</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Fifth part. Small part. Contains some more archery changes, a new level 50 spell for midgard's darkness line, and an addition to the /level command.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/869.php" target="top">1.62F</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Number six. More archer stuff, more Hibernian caster stuff. Also explains the release date for 1.62 (after E3)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/870.php" target="top">1.62G</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Sneaky number seven. Took a look at snares, and tweaked more hibernian caster/hybrids.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/874.php" target="top">1.62H</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Number eight. Some Hibernian Casters stuff, other random things, and a big list of item changes.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/875.php" target="top">1.62I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Nineth addition. A new respec policy, with some more tweaks on the side to random things.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/877.php" target="top">1.62J</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Patch part, number Ten. A few pendragon fixes, and the introduction of the new Newbie Guild.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.camelotherald.com/more/879.php" target="top">1.62K</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Latest patch, number eleven. Fixed the animation for archers, changes a few things for 'em and improves snares.<br>
<br>
That's a lot of parts!!! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
I'll add more parts when/if they release, although I have a feeling number J is our last for this one. <br>
<br>
